</P>
<P>
   CHURCHGOERS REJOICE IN DEFEATING A STATE LOTTERY IN ALABAMA
</P>
<P>
   A6104 BC-MFUME-SCHOOLS14-COX 338 21:49 U A
</P>
<P>
   A6106 BC-EXP-BUCHANAN-REFORM-NYT 504 21:49 U A
</P>
<P>
   BUCHANAN APPEARS TO MOVE CLOSER TO SEEKING REFORM PARTY'S
NOMINATION
