<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-14 02:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6473 &Cx1f; tth-z
u s BC-BBA-VECSEY-COLUMN-SPI     10-14 0844
