<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    UNCERTAINTY OVER PRICES, PROBLEMS RUFFLES MILLENNIUM TRAVEL
 &HT;    Moving in (k) commentary and (t) travel categories for release
Sunday, Oct. 17.
