<P>
   EDs: A Sept. 16 article about Hurricane Floyd incorrectly
reported the extent of damage to the Abaco Inn near Hope Town on
Elbow Cay in the Bahamas. The hotel was damaged but was not washed
away, and reopening is planned for mid-November.
</P>
