<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-14 17:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6980 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-ANTIQUES-COLUMN-ART &LR; -     10-14 1164
