<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-14 19:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7181 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u p BC-GORE-2000-HNS &LR;      10-14 1034
