   (NYT29) NEW YORK -- Oct. 14, 1999 -- BBA-YANKS-REDSOX-4, 10-14
-- Derek Lowe of the Boston Red Sox chatting with some fans in the
outfield stands during practice before Game 2 of the American
League Championship Series against the New York Yankees on
Thursday. The Yankees lead the best-of-7 series 1-0. (Bill
Greene/Boston Globe Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT28) NEW YORK -- Oct. 14, 1999 -- BBA-YANKS-REDSOX-3, 10-14
-- From left, Riche Garces, Pedro Martinez and Jose Offerman of the
Boston Red Sox fooling around during practice before Game 2 of the
