Greene/Boston Globe Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT27) NEW YORK -- Oct. 14, 1999 -- BBA-YANKS-REDSOX-2, 10-14
-- New York Yankees manager Joe Torre, left, and his Boston Red Sox
counterpart, Jimmy Williams, before Game 2 of the American League
Championship Series against the Boston Red Sex at Yankee Stadium on
Thursday. (Barton Silverman/New York Times Photo)
