10-14 -- Amy Abels, sitting on a washing machine, with Erez Maman,
center, and Alain Jachiet after being ordered to evacuate from
their settlement on Thursday. Settlers backed down from threats of
confrontation and agreed not to stand in the way of the evacuation
of 12 West Bank outposts the Israeli government has deemed illegal.
(Rina Castelnuovo/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
