Roddy Doyle, a popular Irish writer who has just written ``A Star
Called Henry.'' The novel is the first installment of an ambitious,
unconventional trilogy that will sum up the tumultuous history of
20th-century Ireland through the life and voice of one character.
(Bill Brett/Boston Globe Photo)
</P>
