<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-14 22:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7419 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-INVEST-ALLSTARS-NYT &LR;      10-14 0668
